headline: Clan Orb
summary:
Founded in 2000, We're a laid back clan for casual gamers. We specialize in cool, down-to-earth adults who consider teamwork and a little humor to be key to having a great time, but don't take it too seriously.

We play WoW predominantly, but we have members from many different games.

If you meet the before-mentioned prerequisites, let us know and play alongside us. Invites are by recommendation of other Orb members only. Asshats need not apply. No invites for profiles with VAC bans. Silly hats only.
